KPI: Average Household Income 12

Household Income

Name Worksheet.

Drag and Drop fields in Text Mark  (Fields,  Household Income, cc. YoY Avg HH Income, cc. Avg HH Income Down , cc. Avg HH Income Up)


Edit as in gif



 Formatting the Labels with Color, Font and Size

1  - Select each field and format it  (Details are given below)

2  - Select Color   

3 - Select More Color     

4 - Copy and paste/type in the given color code   

5 - Click OK

Do the same for each field then  6 Click Apply to see if all of them match that in the snapshot.

If it does Press OK 7 



Format Details 

Avg Household Income  - Size, 8

<AVG(Household Income)> - Size 26, #68344e

<AGG(cc.YoY HH Income DOWN)> - Size 9, #c60000

<AGG(cc.YoY HH Income UP)>  - Size 9,  #59a14f

<AGG(cc.YoY Avg HH Income)> vs PY - Size 9, #676767


Format & De-activate Tooltip

Click Text Mark to Center,  Right click AVG(Household Income) to format, Right Click AGG(cc. YoY Avg HH Income) to Format, Click on Tooltip to de-activate it by unchecking the boxes.
